ukui-media (2.0.3-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream bugfix release.
    - Fix the i18n issue.
    - Fix that the tooltip doesn't disappear.
    - Fix that the slider disapplears when switching music.
    - Fix that sometimes 'mute' doesn't take effect.
    - Fix the incorrect position of popup window.
    - Fix the wrong output volume when insert new card device.
  * debian/watch:
    - Updated to monitor the upstream orig.tar.gz.

